{"title":"Weekend Roundup: Dirt Fund #Senditforward, Ride 100 miles to Win, Bike to Ski & more!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/13/weekend-roundup-dirt-fund-senditforward-ride-100-miles-to-win-bike-to-ski-more/","date":1623627275000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><strong>The DirtFund Project aims to #Senditforward, supporting privateer racers</strong> – We’re more than a tiny bit partial on this one here at Bikerumor (<em>more on that in a second</em>). But we love the idea of supporting grassroots racers looking to step up to the next level. Established just last November by Daniel O’Shea and “a bunch of dirtbag mountain bike mates”, The DirtFund Project turns mountain biker passion into support for up-and-coming local racers.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Qntpno_ZEXM?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.29251898390282904\"></iframe></span></p><p>Run entirely on volunteer labor &amp; as a non-profit effort, the goal is simply “to help privateer EWS &amp; World Cup DH racers from the UK &amp; Ireland fulfill their racing dreams”. For the 2021 race season, this has already developed into the opportunity where money donated by the mountain bike rider community is being converted to one-time cash grants of £1000/1000€ handed directly to several selected privateer racers.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers.jpg\" alt=\"The DirtFund Project aims to #Senditforward, supporting privateer racers\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132818/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>“To date, thanks to the amazing MTB cycling community and some uber cool brands in and around the cycling industry”, The DirtFund has already been able to deliver 5 x 1000 cash grants to help 5 “phenomenal privateer racers” in their path to stepping up their race game.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261737\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261737\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan.jpg\" alt=\"The DirtFund Project aims to #Senditforward, supporting privateer racers, Jessie-May Morgan\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/11132824/The-DirtFund-Project-supporting-privateer-racers_photo-by-Robyn-Wilkinson_our-own-Jessie-May-Morgan-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/